{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/hati-hati-techno-edm-grup-idol-jepang/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Hati Hati Techno Menggabungkan Musik EDM Dengan Keimutan Grup Idol Jepang","content":"<p>Berada di daerah bukan berarti nggak bisa menikmati acara-acara keren, loh! Di Malang misalnya, ada <em>event</em> Jejepangan bernama <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/nostalgia-anime-daisuki-japan-festival-2018/\">Daisuki Japan Festival 2018</a>. Diselenggarakan oleh Japan Culture Daisuki, Daisuki Japan Festival 2018 merupakan salah satu acara Jejepangan terbesar di Malang. Para penggila <em>anime</em>, <em>manga</em>, <em>idol</em>, dan segala hal berbau Jejepangan lainnya berkumpul di UMM Dome pada tanggal 11 Maret 2018 lalu untuk bersenang-senang.</p>\n<p>Daisuki Japan Festival bukan sekedar <em>event</em> Jejepangan daerah saja, karena di tiap tahunnya mereka senantiasa memboyong bintang tamu dari Jepang dan luar negeri! Di tahun ini saja, Japan Culture Daisuki sukses memboyong grup <em>idol</em> <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/daisuki-japan-festival-2018-bertabur-guest-star-lokal-dan-mancanegara/\">Hati Hati Techno</a> ke Malang. Hati Hati Techno merupakan grup <em>idol</em> yang <em>up-and-coming</em>, tak hanya di Jepang namun juga di Indonesia!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_44407\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-44407\" data-attachment-id=\"44407\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/daisuki-japan-festival-2018-bertabur-guest-star-lokal-dan-mancanegara/attachment/dasukii2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/dasukii2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Hati Hati Techno. Sumber: Ameblo.jp\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Hati Hati Techno. Sumber: Ameblo.jp&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/dasukii2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/dasukii2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44407\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/dasukii2.jpg\" alt=\"Hati Hati Techno. Sumber: Ameblo.jp\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/dasukii2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/dasukii2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-44407\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Ameblo</p></div></p>\n<p>Saya mendapatkan kesempatan untuk ngobrol dengan para anggota Hati Hati Techno di sela-sela kesibukan mereka di Daisuki Japan Festival 2018. Seperti apa sih grup J-pop asal Jepang ini? Apa yang mereka lakukan di Indonesia, dan apa yang membedakan mereka dengan grup <em>idol</em> lainnya? Langsung disimak saja, ya!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45057\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45057\" data-attachment-id=\"45057\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/hati-hati-techno-edm-grup-idol-jepang/attachment/01-hati-hati-techno/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-hati-hati-techno\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-hati-hati-techno-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45057\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" alt=\"01 hati hati techno\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-hati-hati-techno.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/01-hati-hati-techno-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45057\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kiri ke kanan: Risa Koizumi, Rui Toya, dan Anju Nagai. (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Hati Hati Techno dibentuk tahun 2017 dengan anggota Risa Koizumi, Rui Toya, dan Anju Nagai. Risa adalah <em>leader</em> dari grup ini, sementara Rui merupakan seorang <em>seiyuu</em> (pengisi suara), dan Anju merupakan penggila Gundam. Mereka bertiga adalah anggota grup Enka Girls, dan Hati Hati Techno merupakan sub grup dari Enka Girls.</p>\n<p>Nama Hati Hati Techno dipilih untuk menonjolkan konsep “KawaEDM” mereka. Dengan konsep tersebut, mereka berharap bisa menarik perhatian masyarakat lewat nama dan penampilan mereka. Tapi, apa sih maksud dari “KawaEDM” itu sendiri? Hati Hati Techno mengusung <em>genre</em> musik unik yang disebut “KawaEDM.” “KawaEDM” sendiri merupakan gabungan dari konsep “<em>kawaii</em>” alias imut dengan <em>genre</em> Electronic Dance Music atau EDM. Risa menyebutkan bahwa “KawaEDM” yang diusung mereka menampilkan musik EDM bertempo tinggi dengan sentuhan keimutan khas grup <em>idol</em> Jepang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45058\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45058\" data-attachment-id=\"45058\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/hati-hati-techno-edm-grup-idol-jepang/attachment/02-hati-hati-techno/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-hati-hati-techno\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-hati-hati-techno-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45058\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" alt=\"02-hati-hati-techno\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-hati-hati-techno.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/02-hati-hati-techno-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45058\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Single perdana Spider Girl. (Sumber: Hati Hati Techno)</p></div></p>\n<p>Hati Hati Techno sudah merilis satu CD <em>single</em>, yaitu Spider Girl. <em>Single</em> ini berisi 4 lagu. Semuanya adalah Spider Girl, Flyby, Driving Night, dan Western Hollywood. Layaknya Enka Girls, grup ini juga diproduseri oleh Kevin Aprilio dari Vierratale. Kevin dan beberapa <em>songwriter</em> berbakat lainnya menjadi otak di balik lagu yang dinyanyikan Risa dan kawan-kawan. Mengikuti Enka Girls yang pernah meng-<em>cover</em> lagu Faith dari Vierratale, Hati Hati Techno juga pernah meng-<em>cover</em> lagu klasik Vierratale, Dengarkan Curhatku dalam <em>genre</em> EDM!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45059\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45059\" data-attachment-id=\"45059\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/hati-hati-techno-edm-grup-idol-jepang/attachment/03-hati-hati-techno/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-hati-hati-techno\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-hati-hati-techno-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45059\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" alt=\"03-hati-hati-techno\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-hati-hati-techno.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/03-hati-hati-techno-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45059\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Hati Hati Techno sudah dua kali tampil di Indonesia, dan yang kedua kalinya inilah mereka tampil di Daisuki Japan Festival di Malang. Meski sudah dua kali tampil di Indonesia, baru pertama kalinya mereka tampil di Jawa Timur. Risa dan kawan-kawan yang cukup fasih berbahasa Indonesia ini merasa gugup tampil di depan khalayak baru, namun mereka berharap penampilan Hati Hati Techno yang membawakan 6 lagu di Daisuki Japan Festival ini bisa memukau pecinta Jejepangan di Malang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45060\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45060\" data-attachment-id=\"45060\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/hati-hati-techno-edm-grup-idol-jepang/attachment/04-hati-hati-techno/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-hati-hati-techno\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-hati-hati-techno-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45060\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" alt=\"04-hati-hati-techno\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-hati-hati-techno.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/04-hati-hati-techno-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45060\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Ke depannya, grup ini berambisi untuk menjadi grup <em>idol</em> populer di Indonesia. Maka dari itu, mereka berencana untuk membuat beberapa lagu <em>cover</em> berbasa Indonesia dengan gaya “KawaEDM” mereka sendiri.</p>\n<p>Selama 1.5 tahun, <em>member</em> Hati Hati Techno sudah 9 kali menyambangi Indonesia, termasuk bersama Enka Girls. Di tahun ini, mereka berniat untuk semakin sering tampil di Indonesia, hingga dua kali lipatnya. Risa, Rui, dan Anju meminta dukungan penuh dari teman-teman di Indonesia agar semakin sukses di Indonesia.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45061\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45061\" data-attachment-id=\"45061\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/hati-hati-techno-edm-grup-idol-jepang/attachment/05-hati-hati-techno/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-hati-hati-techno\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-hati-hati-techno-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45061\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" alt=\"05-hati-hati-techno\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-hati-hati-techno.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/05-hati-hati-techno-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45061\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Pictures</p></div></p>\n<p>Kamu bisa mengikuti <em>update</em> dari Hati Hati Techno melalui akun Twitter dan Instagram mereka di @hatihati_techno, <em>website</em> resmi di hatihati-techno.tokyo, serta <em>blog</em> mereka di <a href=\"http://ameblo.jp/hatihatitechno/\">http://ameblo.jp/hatihatitechno/</a>. Kabar-kabar lain dari Risa, Rui, dan Anju juga bisa kamu simak di <em>fanpage</em> Enka Girls di <a href=\"https://web.facebook.com/enkagirls.official/\">https://web.facebook.com/enkagirls.official/</a></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45062\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45062\" data-attachment-id=\"45062\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/hati-hati-techno-edm-grup-idol-jepang/attachment/06-hati-hati-techno/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-hati-hati-techno\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-hati-hati-techno-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45062\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-hati-hati-techno.jpg\" alt=\"06-hati-hati-techno\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-hati-hati-techno.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/06-hati-hati-techno-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45062\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sehabis makan es krim, mejeng dulu dengan tote bag Heartbeat! (Sumber: CIAYO Pictures)</p></div></p>\n<p>Itu dia <em>chit-chat</em> singkat saya dengan Risa, Rui, dan Anju. Setelahnya, Hati Hati Techno bahkan menyempatkan diri mereka untuk mampir dan mencoba es krim di <em>booth</em> CIAYO Comics! Sukses terus untuk Hati Hati Techno, semoga bisa menjadi salah satu grup <em>idol</em> yang mampu meramaikan skena musik pop Jepang dan juga Indonesia!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"b9c0d163-0df8-5ae5-b151-3f7aceafbdb5"}}}